ğŸ“‰ Line chart â€” Sales Trend by Month
plt.figure(figsize=(8,5))
sales_by_month.plot(kind="line", marker="o")
plt.title("Monthly Sales Trend")
plt.xlabel("Month")
plt.ylabel("Sales")
plt.grid(True)
